      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh-car magic. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously kept, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
