    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered lineage, preserved in museum-grade condition. The 3.2L high-compression inline-six features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with recent valve shim adjustments and a proactively bulletproofed double VANOS system. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, benefitting from a proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. Rolling on period-correct Style 67 forged wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S compound, this vehicle exhibits zero deferred maintenance and factory-spec compression across all six cylinders. A turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
