    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like shine with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of wear or creasing, and still retains that distinct new-car aroma. All interior trim pieces, from the brushed aluminum accents to the high-definition displays, are flawless and fully operational. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its life in a climate-controlled garage. With exceptionally low mileage and a set of pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year.",
      "price": 48500.0,
