      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, and it still looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in spectacular shape\u2014no scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh and looking pristine. It drives like an absolute dream and has been tucked away in a garage whenever it wasn't on the road. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
